public class EnemyPlaneFactory extends PlaneFactory
Factory class for creating enemy planes in the game.

This class extends PlaneFactory and provides methods to create different types of enemy planes based on specific configurations. It supports the creation of both normal and fast enemy planes through the EnemyPlaneFactory.EnemyType enumeration.

    • createEntity

      public GameObject createEntity(double xPos, double yPos, double fastProbability)
      Creates an EnemyPlane instance based on the specified parameters.

      The type of enemy plane (normal or fast) is determined by the specified probability.

      Parameters:
      xPos - the X-coordinate position of the plane.
      yPos - the Y-coordinate position of the plane.
      fastProbability - the probability of spawning a fast enemy plane. A higher value increases the likelihood.
      Returns:
      an EnemyPlane instance with the selected type's configuration.
